  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>successful re-use of isoniazid for TB treatment</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months</time_frame>
    <description>In this study, we would like to test the hypothesis of NAT2 genotyping helping in isoniazid rechallenge after patients experienced adverse effects of anti-TB treatment. Therefore, to observe the patients can re-use isoniazid successfully is an important outcome measure in this study.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
